               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-89ra)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymn (fols. 3ra-6ra)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 6ra-8ra)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fol. 8ra-va)&#xD; I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām
                     "Miracles of Mary": 100 miracles (fols. 8va-89ra)&#xD; I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi ...
                     "Does not the man ..." (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols.
                     15ra-27vb), incomplete (13 strophes)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-1 contains the hymns: salām laki ḫoḫǝta mǝśrāq ... "Salutation to
                        you, Threshold of the East ..." (<locus target="#5va">5va-</locus>vb)
                        <!-- = LIT4714Salamlaki (MV 2017-09-07) -->.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>Text I-2 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām ʾǝmmu la-ʾIyasus Krǝstos kahāli ...
                        "O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..."
                           (<locus target="#7rb">7rb-</locus>va) (cp. ChRep n<locus target="#373">373</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām ʾǝmma madḫǝn wa-ʾǝmma
                        bǝrhān ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of the
                        Saviour and Mother of the Light ..."(<locus from="7va" to="8ra">7va-8ra</locus>).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles of Mary (Text I-4) are numbered (numbers are written in the
                        margins).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>Text I-5 comprises 12 strophes which are strophes 2-7, 22-23, 25, 28-29,
                        33 according to GrohHymn pp. 336-53 and one additional (<locus target="#27va">27va</locus>b):</note>
                     <note>ኢትኅድግኒ፡ ዓቂበ፡ ኵሎ፡ መዓልተ፡ ወሌሊተ።</note>
                     <note>ኀበ፡ ወአልኩ፡ ፍና፡ ወኀበ፡ ኃደርኩ፡ ቤተ።</note>
                     <note>ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ዘትመግቢ፡ ነፍሳተ፡</note>
                     <note>በልብስ፡ ወበሲሳይ፡ ኢታርእዪኒ፡ ንዴተ።</note>
                     <note>እስመ፡ ቍር፡ ወረኃብ፡ ያረስዕ፡ ጸሎተ።</note>
                  </msItem>
